"The `org.springframework.orm.jpa.hibernate` package supersedes the former "
"`orm.hibernate5`: now for use with Hibernate ORM 7.x, tightly integrated "
"with `HibernateJpaVendorAdapter` as well as supporting Hibernate's native "
